---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="TacticalPilot — Onboarding e Automatizacao de Fluxos de Trabalho"
  description="TacticalPilot ajuda empresas a integrar funcionarios com etapas guiadas, permissoes, tarefas baseadas em funcoes e roteamento de solicitacoes CRM — multilingue e adaptado por pais."
  lang="pt"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">TacticalPilot</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">TacticalPilot</Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="tp-hero position-relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="tp-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="tp-container position-relative tp-py-5">
      <div class="tp-row">
        <div class="tp-col-left">
          <div class="tp-pill">
            <span class="tp-dot"></span>
            <span class="tp-pill-text">Beta apenas por convite</span>
            <span class="tp-divider"></span>
            <span class="tp-pill-sub">A plataforma esta ativa e funcionando — o acesso e concedido por convite.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tp-hero-brand">
            <img src="/images/logo.webp" alt="TacticalPilot" class="tp-logo" width="100" height="100" />
            <div>
              <h1 class="tp-title">TacticalPilot</h1>
              <div class="tp-subtitle">CRM de Onboarding e Automatizacao de Fluxos de Trabalho</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="tp-lead">
            Um unico espaco de trabalho para integrar funcionarios, aplicar etapas operacionais, atribuir permissoes e rotear solicitacoes de clientes — multilingue e adaptado por pais.
          </p>
          <div class="tp-badges">
            <span class="tp-badge">Etapas de onboarding</span>
            <span class="tp-badge">Permissoes e grupos</span>
            <span class="tp-badge">Fluxos por funcao</span>
            <span class="tp-badge">Roteamento CRM</span>
            <span class="tp-badge">Multilingue</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tp-buttons">
            <a class="tp-btn-primary" href="mailto:info@tacticalpilot.org?subject=Solicitar%20convite%20(TacticalPilot)">Solicitar convite</a>
            <a class="tp-btn-outline" href="#how-it-works">Como funciona</a>
          </div>
          <div class="tp-contact">
            Contato: <a href="mailto:info@tacticalpilot.org">info@tacticalpilot.org</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tp-col-right">
          <div class="tp-card-glass">
            <div class="tp-card-header">
              <div class="tp-card-title">Ativacao da empresa, de ponta a ponta</div>
              <span class="tp-badge-beta">Beta</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tp-card-mini">Padronize cada nova contratacao e mantenha um registro de auditoria de tarefas, aprovacoes e evidencias.</div>
            <img src="/images/logo.webp" class="tp-card-img" alt="Preview do TacticalPilot" loading="lazy" />
            <ul class="tp-card-list">
              <li>Gerentes definem as etapas necessarias (e-mail, ferramentas, acessos, documentos...).</li>
              <li>Funcionarios completam as etapas em um espaco de trabalho privado e guiado.</li>
              <li>Solicitacoes e excecoes sao roteadas com SLA, notas e evidencias.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Espaco publicitario - Google AdSense</div>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="tp-light" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="tp-container tp-py-5">
      <div class="tp-section-header">
        <div>
          <h2 class="tp-section-title">Como funciona</h2>
          <p class="tp-section-sub">Crie onboarding baseado em funcoes, tarefas orientadas por permissoes e roteamento CRM — em um sistema consistente.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="tp-btn-dark" href="mailto:info@tacticalpilot.org?subject=Solicitar%20demo%20(TacticalPilot)">Solicitar uma demo</a>
      </div>

      <div class="tp-features-grid">
        <div class="tp-feature">
          <div class="tp-icon-light">1</div>
          <h3 class="tp-feature-title">Fluxo de onboarding</h3>
          <p class="tp-feature-text">Crie uma lista de verificacao para cada funcao: contas, alias de e-mail, dispositivos, regras de seguranca, documentos necessarios, etapas especificas por pais.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tp-feature">
          <div class="tp-icon-light">2</div>
          <h3 class="tp-feature-title">Permissoes geram tarefas</h3>
          <p class="tp-feature-text">Atribua permissoes por grupo ou individualmente. Cada permissao pode gerar automaticamente tarefas e aprovacoes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tp-feature">
          <div class="tp-icon-light">3</div>
          <h3 class="tp-feature-title">Roteamento CRM</h3>
          <p class="tp-feature-text">Solicitacoes de clientes sao roteadas ao funcionario/equipe designado, com SLA, status, notas e registro de auditoria.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tp-panels-grid">
        <div class="tp-panel">
          <h3 class="tp-feature-title">Operacoes adaptadas por pais</h3>
          <p class="tp-feature-text">Funcoes e procedimentos podem variar por pais. TacticalPilot suporta regras por pais, etapas obrigatorias e conteudo localizado.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tp-panel">
          <h3 class="tp-feature-title">Multilingue por design</h3>
          <p class="tp-feature-text">Funcionarios de diferentes paises veem etapas e tarefas em seu idioma, enquanto gerentes obteem relatorios unificados.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tp-cta-light">
        <div class="tp-cta-content">
          <div>
            <h2 class="tp-cta-title">TacticalPilot esta ativo (beta)</h2>
            <p class="tp-feature-text">O acesso e atualmente apenas por convite. Envie um e-mail e informe o tamanho da sua empresa e caso de uso para receber um convite.</p>
          </div>
          <a class="tp-btn-primary" href="mailto:info@tacticalpilot.org?subject=Solicitar%20convite%20(TacticalPilot)">Solicitar convite</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Espaco publicitario - Google AdSense</div>

  <section class="tp-footer-info">
    <div class="tp-footer-licence">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Tactical Pilot. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <p>Endereco: Noregon - London (KI)</p>
      <p><strong>N.o da Licenca:</strong> KBN-40-000003</p>
      <p>Autoridade: Kiribati International Financial Authority (KIFA)</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jura:wght@300..700&display=swap');
</style>

<style>
  :root {
    --tp-bg: #0b0c10;
    --tp-card: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    --tp-border: rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    --tp-text: rgba(255,255,255,.86);
    --tp-muted: rgba(255,255,255,.62);
  }

  .tp-container { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .tp-py-5 { padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem; }

  /* HERO */
  .tp-hero {
    color: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    font-family: 'Jura', sans-serif;
  }
  .tp-hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: -2px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(800px 400px at 20% 20%, rgba(80,120,255,.35), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(600px 380px at 80% 30%, rgba(170,60,255,.28), transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(700px 500px at 55% 95%, rgba(40,220,160,.18), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.03), rgba(255,255,255,0));
    filter: saturate(1.05);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .tp-row {
    display: flex; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .tp-col-left { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
  .tp-col-right { flex: 0 0 380px; min-width: 280px; }
  @media(max-width:900px) { .tp-col-right { flex: 1 1 100%; } }

  .tp-pill {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    border-radius: 999px; padding: 8px 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: .85rem;
  }
  .tp-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #4cffb5;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(76,255,181,.16);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .tp-divider {
    width: 1px; height: 16px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
  }
  .tp-pill-text { font-weight: 600; }
  .tp-pill-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }

  .tp-hero-brand {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .tp-logo {
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
    padding: 10px;
  }
  .tp-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Jura', sans-serif;
  }
  .tp-subtitle { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }

  .tp-lead {
    color: var(--tp-text); max-width: 54ch;
    font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .tp-badges {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .tp-badge {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
    padding: .55rem .7rem; border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: .85rem;
  }

  .tp-buttons { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .tp-btn-primary {
    display: inline-block; border-radius: 14px;
    padding: .85rem 1.2rem;
    background: #0d6efd; color: #fff; border: none;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .tp-btn-primary:hover { background: #0b5ed7; text-decoration: none; }
  .tp-btn-outline {
    display: inline-block; border-radius: 14px;
    padding: .85rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.92); background: transparent;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .tp-btn-outline:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }

  .tp-contact { font-size: .85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }
  .tp-contact a { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); }

  /* GLASS CARD */
  .tp-card-glass {
    background: var(--tp-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--tp-border);
    border-radius: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .tp-card-header {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tp-card-title { font-weight: 600; }
  .tp-badge-beta {
    background: #f8f9fa; color: #333;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);
  }
  .tp-card-mini { color: var(--tp-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: .9rem; }
  .tp-card-img { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); }
  .tp-card-list {
    margin-top: 16px; padding-left: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
  }
  .tp-card-list li { margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: .9rem; }

  /* HOW IT WORKS - LIGHT SECTION */
  .tp-light {
    background: #f4f5f7; color: #111;
    font-family: 'Jura', sans-serif;
  }
  .tp-section-header {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .tp-section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tp-section-sub { color: #666; margin: 0; }

  .tp-btn-dark {
    display: inline-block; border-radius: 14px;
    padding: .85rem 1.05rem;
    background: #111; color: #fff; border: none;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .tp-btn-dark:hover { background: #222; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }

  .tp-features-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  @media(max-width:768px) { .tp-features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .tp-feature {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    border-radius: 22px; padding: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
  }
  .tp-icon-light {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 14px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);
    color: #111; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tp-feature-title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tp-feature-text { color: #666; margin: 0; font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.5; }

  .tp-panels-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  @media(max-width:768px) { .tp-panels-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .tp-panel {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    border-radius: 22px; padding: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }

  .tp-cta-light {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    border-radius: 22px; padding: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .tp-cta-content {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
  }
  .tp-cta-title { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .tp-footer-info {
    background: var(--tp-bg); color: var(--tp-text);
    text-align: center; padding: 24px 0;
    font-family: 'Jura', sans-serif;
  }
  .tp-footer-licence { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: .85rem; }
  .tp-footer-licence p { margin: 4px 0; }

  /* Override BaseLayout for dark sections */
  .ad-slot {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04) !important;
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.1) !important;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.5) !important;
  }
</style>
